    {\displaystyle \forall j:j\neq C_{k}\rightarrow bit(j,A_{k+1})=bit(j,A_{k})}
  . Note that at the first 
  
    
      
        
          n
          
            1
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle n_{1}}
   steps, 
  
    
      
