          Π
          
            p
          
          
            0
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \Pi _{p}^{0}}
  . After moving to prenex formal form the new 
  
    
      
        φ
        (
        n
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle \varphi (n)}
   is in 
  
    
      
        
          Σ
          
            p
            +
